{"tid":1844510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港末日將至","createTime":"2020-01-26T16:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T23:15:03.000Z","uid":92881,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad06202ac3f4130d73a57ec9dd77833d27c1ff7","tid":1844510,"uid":92881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"1）全國都封關，許出不許入；香港不封關<br />\n2）全國醫院不收症；香港醫院收<br />\n<br />\n如果你係新感染者，你會去邊度？<br />\n<br />\n根本大陸仆街政府呢一著，就係想將所有武漢肺炎既病患由全國各城各省各市各縣迫晒黎香港，即係香港係棄子，棄香港保全國。一個人口密度咁高既城市，如果有以萬計既感染者入境，香港700萬人等死罷啦。<br />\n<br />\n預計「全國封關香港不封」既消息傳開之後，會比一段時間新感染者黎香港，之後香港就會封關，將所有感染者contain係香港。<br />\n<br />\n咁你班香港人都睇唔明，人地講明係戰爭模式咁打，即係捉一盤棋，以全國既格局去做病毒圍堵 （containment），咁搵邊個城市做犧牲品？親疏有別，全國各地都有中央高官既自己人，要犧牲當然係犧牲香港啦！而且仲有班白痴狗官、藍絲同建制派，比人當condom都唔知，仲講咩「大家都係一家人，唔可以封關既」，仲有啲黑警係微博係咁呼籲佢地啲內地粉絲黎香港醫肺炎，話「香港的大門永遠會你們打開」，真係話你on居怕你嬲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a877a35a4964151b2ae2775072ee0d658372710d","tid":1844510,"uid":92881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"7beaeca49db725870b7fba3ea36ac2b992f717ff","tid":1844510,"uid":92881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"e123b896b4f3d212f6